A gentlemen would at least offer
to buy me a drink first.

26
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:15,450
Newman, a pint of bitter for me
and a brandy for the lady, please.

27
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,770
- How did you know that?
- Lucky guess.

28
