Infinite forms of variation with each generation.

42
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:53,320
All through, mutation.

43
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:56,350
Then let's reclaim that word.

44
00:11:00,050 --> 00:11:02,300
- Mutant and proud.
- Chin, chin, hey.

45
