Hi, I guess I have to buy my own drink.

46
00:11:04,350 --> 00:11:05,370
I'm sorry, one cola.

47
00:11:05,490 --> 00:11:06,510
Charles here was just telling me that I'm

48
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:08,660
like one of the first sea creatures that grew legs.

49
00:11:08,660 --> 00:11:09,990
Tiny bit sexier.

50
00:11:10,530 --> 00:11:12,340
I'm sorry, this is my sister, Raven.

51
00:11:13,350 --> 00:11:16,310
-Hi, Amy.
-And what do you study?

52
00:11:16,310 --> 00:11:18,650
- Waitressing.
- Aah.

53
