Oh look, you have heterochromia too!

54
00:11:23,310 --> 00:11:25,450
- Say what?
- Look at her eye..

55
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:30,700
Right, Raven get your coat please.

56
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,240
Don't talk to me, you did
that on purpose.

57
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,570
- I did not!
- Yes you did!

58
00:11:34,660 --> 00:11:37,060
Why would I do it on purpose?
You know I can't control it sometimes.

59
00:11:37,170 --> 00:11:40,100
- When I'm stressed or tired..
- You seem to be doing a perfectly
good job right now.

60
00:11:40,690 --> 00:11:42,510
"Mutant and proud"

61
